comments: This guy is a really good teacher because he\'s totally real and honest with the class. He knows who is learning and who isn\'t. If you\'ve proved to him that you know the material it\'s likely you won\'t need to take the final.

He is an awesome teacher. He knows what he is teaching and actually has experience. He doesn\'t just define and talk out of the book, he explains everything through his own experiences in the field. He is an awesome teacher and the best teacher I have had yet and this is my last semester at FCC. Take his class!
TAKE NOTES! Definitions are key! He does not like to give tests in the test center if you miss a test day, Take them notes down the hall - Easy A.

Mr. Williams is an excellent teacher! My class was a 3 week summer course - based on PP lectures. He tells you everything that will be on the test so you know what to study. This was a very interesting and fun class, if you want to enjoy learning psychology and get an easy A take PSY101 with Mr. Williams!

LOVED HIM. He made it really clear what we needed to know for the tests. The research paper was easy. He is a very easy grader. Sometimes he can be really boring, but he tells a lot of stories and has a good sense of humor. If you want an easy A, take him!
Easy grader, overall easy class and Williams has an interesting sense of humor. class is very boring though, did not enjoy it very much.
Very helpful and understanding. Grades papers eaily! Awesome teacher.

I took two classes with him and i love that he cuts the crap and just lectures what you need to learn! no websites to go to, no pointless worksheets to do, he tells you what you need to know and lets you take it from there! love him!

I took Human Growth and Development, Prof Williams was awesome. He cut out the unnecessary stuff and was extremely straight forward. He goes over the important slide number in his powerpoints the day before the test, so you know what to study. Nice guy, and if you get above a 95% you\'ll get excused from the Final!

HAD HIM PS 101 AND HUMAN GROWTH DEVELOPMENT, LOVED HIM, EASY TO GET AN A BECAUSE HE CUTS OUT THE EXTRA STUFF YOU DONT NEED TO KNOW AND MAKES IT INTERESTING, HE IS PASSIONATE AND FUNNY, REALISTIC, UNDERSTANDS TESTS ARE NOT EVERYONE\'S FORTE GIVES OPPORTUNITIES TO BRING UP GRADE, SHOW UP TO CLASS!!!
Great teacher. Very clear. Fair on exams. Lets you know material before hand. Very nice.
Professor Williams is awesome! He\'s very funny, and very understanding, he is down to earth, and gives honest examples of everything he teaches. Ne is an awesome teacher, best at FCC!

Ridiculously understanding and forgiving. I missed one large assignment that was worth around 10-15% of my grade and made it up by simply doing 2 extra credit assignments that were much easier! Great guy that loves to bash his ex-wives :D
